{"tid":1766070,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"若要勇武，必先習武；平日無行動，就自己做運動","createTime":"2019-12-02T10:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T02:53:47.000Z","uid":293677,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73e0247988ccb695737c8e720ede7911ccd1b1ca","tid":1766070,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是咁的<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">古語有云：修身齊家治國平天下<br />\n要做大事，就要先裝備好自己</span><br />\n只係想提醒手足<span style=\"color: red;\">呢場係長期戰爭</span><br />\n呢場革命運動唔知幾時完<br />\n但係我希望大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">平日要抽時間出黎<br />\n段練身體提升自己既體能</span><br />\n<br />\n大方向就係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民運動，全民健身，<br />\n然後全民習武，<br />\n最後達至&quot;全民勇武&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你唔打得 都起要跑得<br />\n滅少補擒獲既機會</span><br />\n香港人唔洗服兵役<br />\n長期以來又賤視體育運動科目<br />\n又成日打機做御宅族<br />\n搞到個個體能好差<br />\n上到戰場<br />\n淨係個心勇係唔夠架<br />\n人數再多都係散兵游勇<br />\n<br />\n引用普京一句說話：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>沒有實力的憤怒是毫無意義的</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：自知體能太弱，上到戰場只係做炮灰<br />\n小弟從六月已經開始舉鐵，之後買埋奶粉飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，運動<br />\n香港人，健身<br />\n香港人，習武</span>"},{"pid":"3175c5ea6d506ad7a6789ef6aa3b8c77a43323ed","tid":1766070,"uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"附上J圖一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEFQDZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEFQDZ8.png&h=17232a5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93bbd8d8fa13c2925ff8943f38fde093ed32b87b","tid":1766070,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"00933ce3b27353ddc3ee33ed34f716f58527f459","tid":1766070,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bb3df2d3791f35dc670b7c5a16104b924e263a1","tid":1766070,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"好重要！"},{"pid":"4aedae390dc43d2d6b639551845b309278fb1654","tid":1766070,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45df9bea55639dd0c6e09668595c8d5e4c9a1db0","tid":1766070,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}